name: Half a Turkey
description:
Single-colour handmade Gocco screen-printed Christmas card with envelope.

15 x 10.5 cm

Other colours are available in this design.

10% of all proceeds  will be donated to Barnado's Childrens Charity

As the UK’s leading children’s charity, thousands of vulnerable children depend on Barnardo's. Your donation helps ensure they receive the long-term care and support they need this Christmas and throughout the year.
